HEADWORD: Tribalism
<hw>Trib"al*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of
existing in tribes; also, tribal feeling; tribal prejudice or
exclusiveness; tribal peculiarities or characteristics.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

